{"title_page": "Sicily", "text_new": "{{About|the region of Italy}}\n{{Redirect|Sicilia|the Roman province|Sicilia (Roman province)|the Italian film about Sicily|Sicilia!}}\n{{Pp-move-indef}}\n{{EngvarB|date=July 2019}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=July 2019}}\n{{short description|Island in the Mediterranean and region of Italy}}\n{{Infobox settlement\n<!-- See Template:Infobox settlement for additional fields and descriptions -->\n| official_name           = Sicily\n| native_name             = ''Sicilia''\n| native_name_lang        = it\n| settlement_type         = [[Autonomous regions with special statute|Autonomous region of Italy]]\n| short_description       = Autonomous region of Italy\n| image_skyline           = \n| image_alt               = \n| image_caption           = \n| image_flag              = Sicilian Flag.svg\n| flag_alt                = \n| image_shield            = Coat of arms of Sicily.svg\n| shield_size             = 50px\n| shield_alt              = \n| image_blank_emblem      = \n| blank_emblem_size       = \n| blank_emblem_type       = \n| blank_emblem_alt        = \n| nickname                = \n| motto                   = \n| anthem                  = ''[[Madreterra]]''\n| image_map               = Sicily in Italy.svg\n| mapsize                 = \n| map_alt                 = \n| map_caption             = \n| pushpin_map             = \n| pushpin_label_position  = \n| pushpin_map_alt         = \n| pushpin_mapsize         = \n| pushpin_map_caption     = \n| coordinates             = \n| coor_pinpoint           = \n| coordinates_footnotes   = \n| subdivision_type        = Country\n| subdivision_name        = [[Italy]]\n| established_title       = \n| established_date        = \n| founder                 = \n| named_for               = \n| seat_type               = Capital\n| seat                    = [[Palermo]]\n| government_footnotes    = \n| government_type         = \n| leader_party            = [[Diventer\u00e0 Bellissima|DB]]\n| leader_title  